### Verbo GET – listar todos
GET http://localhost:8000/funcionario/ HTTP/1.1
### Verbo GET – listar um
GET http://localhost:8000/funcionario/10 HTTP/1.1
### Verbo POST – adicionar
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/funcionario/ HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

### listar todos com filtro
GET http://localhost:8000/funcionario/?skip=0&limit=100&id=1&nome=ze&matricula=123&cpf=1&grupo=2%2C1&telefone=49 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

